ike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9da2b051cedb7b474f51483dd1bad60f4e3014ed","tid":2119140,"uid":361846,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0c16a41eadc22d10d3811b518363177cb2754362","tid":2119140,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"第一手唔係應該轉右咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:07:56.000Z","msg":"右完要扭盡左軚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"第一手要向盡右高極力子等架車向前行<br />\n你Feel到佢開始快就brake同落極力子<br />\n等你可以夠時間回盡左"},{"pid":"e0173bba738bfe39a37991578bfa888f4044534d","tid":2119140,"uid":361846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce4881184ac2cb29d75b3e7d4296aa9784ef023b","tid":2119140,"uid":88256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎..極力子真係要靠feel<br />\n果度小小暗斜 後波小心d唔好溜就ok"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"如果我第二手軚，入後波，架車向前，想架車向後，極力子應吊高啲嗎？"},{"pid":"5b00149e3ff511f3072d589fccfafbc63c25abee","tid":2119140,"uid":262914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"換左師傅先"},{"pid":"62924ef6244f70e0a5f65474ef10b2e89097142d","tid":2119140,"uid":231179,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:22:57.000Z","msg":"當你貨 Van 先<br />\n天光道斜路調頭應該係常樂街<br />\n<br />\n1. 首先靠晒左然後用最快速度扭盡右軚，務求轉得越多越好，到右邊欄桿前停定，拉手掣，入空波。<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果 step 1 做得好，你車頭應該微微向下，入後波吊極力子直至 feel 到架車震 (即係手掣拉唔住架車咁)，你就可以放手掣加比少少油，再快扭盡左軚，尾唔需要太貼欄桿就可以停，拉手掣，入空波。<br />\n<br />\n3. 入一波，鬆手掣，慢放極力子，拉返直架車入返左線。<br />\n<br />\n4. 去到路口前(停線)踩腳掣收慢架車，再踩極力子停車，拉手掣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n打燈擰頭果 d 我唔講了，你識做啦。"},{"pid":"7896d394e76382d88fb96b1b226372cbfeb68b58","tid":2119140,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:24:35.000Z","msg":"有時向前衝有時向後衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2af038133e5e301b9989e4217d851939db5865e","tid":2119140,"uid":289449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:24:41.000Z","msg":"其實你係未摸熟極力子唔倒後又唔會衝前果個位，而且學車時斜路perfer用拉手制代替break，我師父2樣都有教，不過佢話考試上落斜停0.1秒都好，幾手軑做乜7都好，你一定係用手制"},{"pid":"53379bac3b5e01f7fe52dc0dd44b6b073e9d31fa","tid":2119140,"uid":121270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:25:20.000Z","msg":"車速慢 馱盤快 用腳制控制速度 唔係用極力子"},{"pid":"eb8a9a9e4786224af83cdc0f09a79deece6d0e24","tid":2119140,"uid":101865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"有冇天光道好師傅推介？自動波van<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f403780a1c59a5f99664eecca99540f3f4f723cf","tid":2119140,"uid":36049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"準備定5K重考實際D"},{"pid":"8cae5de343af1992d009d7e5e3abddb6fc3b53f2","tid":2119140,"uid":88256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0173bba738bfe39a37991578bfa888f4044534d","tid":2119140,"uid":361846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce4881184ac2cb29d75b3e7d4296aa9784ef023b","tid":2119140,"uid":88256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎..極力子真係要靠feel<br />\n果度小小暗斜 後波小心d唔好溜就ok"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"如果我第二手軚，入後波，架車向前，想架車向後，極力子應吊高啲嗎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T03:33:36.000Z","msg":"Yes 因為吊得越高越有力  但要小心唔好太大力 過暗斜又會變好快<br />\n準確黎講果度係個倒V咁嘅feel 冇信心就去做多幾次就明個感覺<br />\n記得真係考果陣最緊要慢 唔好覺得阻住人 你考牌你大曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f22f70e0e924f6fc5e